lines.text: Don't you want to try counseling.
It's far too expensive. Not that kind of split up!
Dream boat... that's what she'll say when she sees me...
When I see you, I think tug boat
Well Stanley, when you're the biggest dog on the porch, no one will care how loud you bark!
Your bark is worse than your over-bite...
Say, when you were in Egypt, did you happen to see the Eifel Tower?
Stanley, The Eiffel Tower is not in Egypt... it's in Indiana!
